    <script>
      if ('serviceWorker' in navigator) {
          if (location.search.indexOf('__testServiceWorkers=1') > -1) {
              navigator.serviceWorker.register('/service-worker.js').then(function(reg) {
                  console.log('[SW] Service Worker registered', reg);
              }).catch(function(err) {
                  console.log('[SW] Could not register Service Worker', err);
              });
          } else if (navigator.serviceWorker.getRegistrations) {
              navigator.serviceWorker.getRegistrations().then(function(registrations) {
                  try {
                      for (var registrationKey in registrations) {
                          if (registrations.hasOwnProperty(registrationKey)) {
                              var registration = registrations[registrationKey];
                              registration.unregister();
                          }
                      }
                  } catch (e) { console.error(e); }
              });
          }
      }
    </script>
